{"_response_info":{"status":"ok"},"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/retinal-treatment-and-driving.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/retinal-treatment-and-driving","title":"Retinal treatment and driving","format":"answer","details":{"need_id":"2343","business_proposition":false,"alternative_title":"","overview":"You may need to tell DVLA if you've had retinal treatment - download the correct form if you need to let them know","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>You may need to tell <abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr> if you’ve had retinal treatment.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice help-notice\">\n<p>You can be fined up to £1,000 if you don’t tell <abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr> about a medical treatment or condition that affects your driving. If you’re involved in an accident, you may be prosecuted.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Car or motorcycle licence</h2>\n\n<h3>If you&rsquo;ve had retinal treatment in one eye</h3>\n\n<p>You don&rsquo;t need to tell <abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. </p>\n\n<h3>If you&rsquo;ve had retinal treatment in both eyes</h3>\n\n<p>You must tell <abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. Fill in form V1 and send it to <abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. The address is on the form.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/@motor/documents/digitalasset/dg_065620.pdf\" title=\"Download 'V1 - Confidential medical information' (PDF, 253KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘V1 - Confidential medical information’ (PDF, 253KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Bus, coach or lorry driving licence</h2>\n\n<p>You must tell <abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. Fill in form V1V and send it to the address on the form.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/@motor/documents/digitalasset/dg_065275.pdf\" title=\"Download 'V1V - Confidential medical information' (PDF, 261KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘V1V - Confidential medical information’ (PDF, 261KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n"},"updated_at":"2012-10-16T10:14:47+00:00","tags":[{"title":"Directgov","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/directgov.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":null,"type":"legacy_source"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=directgov","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/directgov"},"parent":null}],"related":[{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/driving-if-disabled.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/driving-if-disabled","title":"Medical conditions, disabilities and driving","format":"guide","details":{"need_id":"786","business_proposition":false},"updated_at":"2012-10-16T10:20:40+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/health-conditions-and-driving.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/health-conditions-and-driving","title":"Health conditions and driving","format":"answer","details":{"need_id":"13","business_proposition":false},"updated_at":"2012-10-16T10:25:48+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/giving-up-your-driving-licence.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/giving-up-your-driving-licence","title":"Giving up your driving licence","format":"answer","details":{"need_id":"2390","business_proposition":false},"updated_at":"2012-10-16T10:17:07+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/reapply-driving-licence-medical-condition.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/reapply-driving-licence-medical-condition","title":"Re-apply for a driving licence following a medical condition","format":"answer","details":{"need_id":"2399","business_proposition":true},"updated_at":"2012-10-16T10:15:05+00:00"}]}